Package control.fileloading.levels.storestructures

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    EntitiesInfoStore
    That interface extends EntitiesInfo(the interface for the communication structure to model) to add setters, this is very helpful for elaboration of entities during the file loading.
    LevelInfo
    Interface that declare all methods of a working object that contains level informations.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EntitiesInfoStoreImpl
    Implementation of EntitiesInfoStore with protected getters and a clone constructor.
    LevelInfoImpl
    Class that contains all informations about a playable level.
    MovementInfoStore
    Class that contains entities' movement traits with setters.
    ShootInfoStore
    Class that contains entities' shoot traits with setters.
